anchor tag
it is used to apply internal and external routing

1) external routing
<a href="">link</a>
  a) absolute  ---like an external source or complete path  c:/drive/internal/fronted/day1/
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML">html external link</a>

  b) relative--local to the project
    <a href="about.html">html external link</a>

